            <title>[MAHOUT-1433] Make SVDRecommender look at all unknown items of a user per default</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1433</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We had a discussion on the mailinglist that (correctly) stated that SVDRecommender should consider all items the user has not interacted with as candidates to recommend per default. This patch changes the default CandidateItemsStrategy for SVDRecommender to realize that.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
